RE: Independent Learning (only WRP) for September 15-20, 2025

Hello Tams!

I’ve been seeing some students that are confused when it comes to the modality for next week.

Only WRP courses from 3rd to 5th year will be on Independent Study.

Other courses and programs (except those not included from the blended learning modality) will continue the blended setup.

Hoping this clears the confusion for some. For further clarifications, don’t hesitate to send me a DM and the rest of the Executive Board!

Thank you!

- FEU CSO President

message.text:
HEYYY IABF TAMSS!!!

Are you interested in editing or illustrations? Or baka naman ur interested in becoming a Canva Master?

I've been part of IABFSC Creatives since my freshman year, and I can say with all my heart that it was the best decision I made. Not only did I develop my creativity and layout skills, but I was also able to make new friends who supported my achievements throughout. 

It wouldn't be an exaggeration to say that IABF SC became my second home. The people and the experiences I made in IABF SC were the BEST MOMENTS OF MY COLLEGE!! medj oa pakingan pero words can't even describe how happy I am to be part of this council. They brought out the best version of myself. 

Joining the Creatives Division brought out my confidence. It's not simply about editing, it's about the feeling of being appreciated by something you do and being able to help the IABF community. 

I want to make more memorable moments with you guyss, sooo if ur interested JOINN NAAA!!!

Ano pa hinihintay niyo? JOIN FEU IABF Student Council Creatives na!!

Share ko na rin sainyo some of my works baka mamotivate kayo to joinn!!

IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M

message.text:
HEYYY IABF TAMSS!!!

Are you interested in editing or illustrations? Or baka naman ur interested in becoming a Canva Master?

I've been part of IABFSC Creatives since my freshman year, and I can say with all my heart that it was the best decision I made. Not only did I develop my creativity and layout skills, but I was also able to make new friends who supported my achievements throughout. 

It wouldn't be an exaggeration to say that IABF SC became my second home. The people and the experiences I made in IABF SC were the BEST MOMENTS OF MY COLLEGE!! medj oa pakingan pero words can't even describe how happy I am to be part of this council. They brought out the best version of myself. 

Joining the Creatives Division brought out my confidence. It's not simply about editing, it's about the feeling of being appreciated by something you do and being able to help the IABF community. 

I want to make more memorable moments with you guyss, sooo if ur interested JOINN NAAA!!!

Ano pa hinihintay niyo? JOIN FEU IABF Student Council Creatives na!!

Share ko na rin sainyo some of my works baka mamotivate kayo to joinn!!

IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M

message.text:
HEYYY IABF TAMSS!!!

Are you interested in editing or illustrations? Or baka naman ur interested in becoming a Canva Master?

I've been part of IABFSC Creatives since my freshman year, and I can say with all my heart that it was the best decision I made. Not only did I develop my creativity and layout skills, but I was also able to make new friends who supported my achievements throughout. 

It wouldn't be an exaggeration to say that IABF SC became my second home. The people and the experiences I made in IABF SC were the BEST MOMENTS OF MY COLLEGE!! medj oa pakingan pero words can't even describe how happy I am to be part of this council. They brought out the best version of myself. 

Joining the Creatives Division brought out my confidence. It's not simply about editing, it's about the feeling of being appreciated by something you do and being able to help the IABF community. 

I want to make more memorable moments with you guyss, sooo if ur interested JOINN NAAA!!!

Ano pa hinihintay niyo? JOIN FEU IABF Student Council Creatives na!!

Share ko na rin sainyo some of my works baka mamotivate kayo to joinn!!

IABF SC Application: https://bit.ly/4mQgw3M
